{"tid":676670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋樹人,心理測試","createTime":"2018-05-24T14:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T18:26:14.000Z","uid":185196,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"84d9e756a0a632fa53c5fec46ec9171c48eb13fe","tid":676670,"uid":185196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"經常睇好多心理學書,想同大家玩呢個測驗<br />\n反映一下準唔準都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋樹人,可以反映自己嘅心理狀態,會將你潛意浮面.透過潛意識自己個腦會自動組識<br />\n自己嘅經歷觀感去了解自己<br />\n屋樹人仲可以自己點樣睇自己同埋同屋企人嘅關係<br />\n<br />\n1.準備一張白紙<br />\n2.想點畫就點畫跟住你個心去畫<br />\n3.畫人嘅時候唔可以畫火柴人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/222459_2a45270cab9cebf9a2d25e2f36b35d89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F222459_2a45270cab9cebf9a2d25e2f36b35d89.jpg&h=1288731e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我會好細心咁分析之後同返你哋講個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bec988c917f7e8fef5ce864af5932c197c69a3","tid":676670,"uid":57159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/223204_5a1f40faab25b5bd23abe7960f6a0c43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F223204_5a1f40faab25b5bd23abe7960f6a0c43.png&h=88a4bbc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46fd3f11cab5b59bba6fa9a9bafedea46edae5cf","tid":676670,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/222459_2a45270cab9cebf9a2d25e2f36b35d89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F222459_2a45270cab9cebf9a2d25e2f36b35d89.jpg&h=1288731e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb75